                             Latin Phrases I Fancy
                             =====================
                      (and other useful/general ones too)

   Let's jump right into it. I may write up a pronunciation guide later on.
  (Letters with an underscore immediately following it can be read as that
   letter with a horizontal bar above it. e.g. a_ denotes 'ā' .)

